(41, 11, 10, 26, 34, 23, 24, 'kingdom of our father David', 'Connection of David''s Kingship', 'Both passages emphasize the role of David as a leader. Mark 11:10 refers to the kingdom of David, while Ezekiel 34:23-24 speaks of David as a shepherd. This connection highlights the continuity of David''s significance in God''s plan.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 11, 10, 30, 9, 11, 12, 'kingdom of our father David', 'Connection of David''s Kingdom', 'This connection highlights the theme of the restoration of David''s lineage and kingdom. Both passages emphasize the significance of David''s name and the hope for a renewed reign that brings blessings.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
