(41, 11, 13, 42, 10, 31, 31, NULL, 'Observation of Unfulfilled Expectations', 'This connection highlights the theme of unmet expectations. In Mark, the fig tree appears promising but yields nothing, while in Luke, the priest sees a man in need but chooses to pass by, both illustrating a failure to fulfill potential.', 'theme', 0.3, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
